    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Package::Stash</title>

      <para>
        Manipulating stashes (Perl's symbol tables) is occasionally necessary,
        but incredibly messy, and easy to get wrong. This module hides all of
        that behind a simple API.
      </para>

